data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!!! This charming ranch-style home in Venetian Villa sits on a quiet cul-de-sac and boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. As you step inside, you'll find a spacious main living area that sets a cozy tone with its beautiful wood-burning fireplace--a perfect addition for creating a warm and inviting ambiance on those chilly evenings. Throughout the entire home, laminate flooring not only ensures easy maintenance but also adds a touch of modern elegance. The updated bathrooms are designed with contemporary finishes and fixtures, offering both comfort and convenience to enhance your daily routine. When it's time to relax, step onto your private screened-in porch-- a true oasis that allows you to savor the outdoors without the annoyance of bugs. Families and pet owners will appreciate the security of the divided fenced backyard, making it an ideal space for outdoor activities and gatherings. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing an excellent space for entertaining guests or keeping an eye on family activities. The kitchen is equipped with a state-of-the-art oven, complete with an air fryer option, simplifying meal preparation and adding a touch of modern convenience to your culinary adventures. This home is centrally located to just about everything in town AND move in ready. Make sure you check this one out today!
